{{not to be confused|fire base}}
In [[military terminology]], a '''base of fire''' is a supporting force that provides [[overwatch (military tactic)|overwatch]] and [[covering fire]] to other advancing units while they are executing [[fire and movement]] tactics. A base of fire can be a [[platoon]] during company fire and movement, by individual [[armoured fighting vehicle]]s (esp. [[tank]]s) or infantry [[Section (military unit)|sections]], in platoon fire and movement, or even by [[fireteam]]s or individual soldiers, in the final stages of an assault.{{Citation needed|date=July 2012}}

