{{for|the token used by Alcoholics Anonymous members|Sobriety coin}} '''Red chips''' stocks ({{zh|t=紅籌股|s=红筹股|p=hóngchóugǔ|y=hung4 chau4 gu2}}) are the stocks of [[mainland China]] companies [[Incorporation (business)|incorporated]] outside mainland China and [[listed company|listed]] in [[Hong Kong]]. These [[business]]es are based in mainland China and controlled, either directly or indirectly, by the central, provincial or municipal governments of the [[China|People's Republic of China]] but listed in Hong Kong to allow overseas investment in the companies.
